description.text: Automatic backups are currently disabled. Infrastructure backups have not been created in the past 24 hours. This warning will appear every 24 hours until the issue is resolved.

remediation.text: 1. Address the issues that require the automatic backups to be disabled.
2. After all issues preventing backups are resolved, navigate to infrastructure backup and configure the settings to enable automatic backups.
